            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3j0009-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_025-33a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-04-28T23:51:52.087+09:00">whom they resent.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_001-22a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-05-14T21:05:50.422+09:00">Eben, sag ich doch, dass ist doch nicht der Mozi</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_021-26a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-22T21:10:43.487+09:00">was able thereby to become...</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_002-21a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-25T22:25:06.923+09:00">With their ears they cannot hear</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_002-21a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-25T22:25:15.789+09:00">with their eyes they cannot see</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_002-21a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-25T22:25:59.923+09:00">with their mouths they cannot eat</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_022-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-06-11T18:43:33.702+09:00">wanted to have him too killed</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_016-36a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-06-26T17:19:31.751+09:00">As a matter of principle misrule</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_016-36a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-06-26T17:20:24.272+09:00">is because punishments and honorary titles are not adequately deployed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_020-15a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-07-12T18:20:11.845+09:00">human individuals</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_013-27a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-02T07:54:38.085+09:00">is that not absurdly unrealistic?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_017-12a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-17T17:57:09.467+09:00">In this way this maintains that ears, eyes, mind and intelligence are not sufficient to RELY on:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_017-12a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-17T17:56:30.231+09:00"/>
                </p>
            </div>
